      • Person

        public Person(java.lang.String name,
              java.lang.String email,
              java.lang.String password,
              java.util.Date dob,
              double height,
              double weight,
              char gender,
              int exercise)
        Creates a Person with the desired attributes.
        Parameters:
        name - user's name.
        age - user's age.
        height - user's height in cm.
        weight - user's weight in kg.
        gender - user's gender M being male and F being female.
        exercise - user's exercise per week:\n 0 = Desk job with little exercise\n 1 = 1-3hrs/week of light exercise\n 2 = 3-5hrs/week of moderate exercise\n 3 = 5-6hrs/week of strenuous exercise\n 4 = 7-21hrs/week of strenuous exercise/work
